text: The Nun II is a 2023 American supernatural horror movie directed by Michael Chaves from a script by Akela Cooper. It is a sequel to The Nun (2018) and The Nun III (2024), thus being the ninth installment of The Conjuring Universe franchise. Taissa Farmiga and Bonnie Aarons reprise their lead roles as Sister Irene and Valak, respectively. The Nun II was released in the United States by Warner Bros. Pictures on September 8, 2023. It has grossed $158 million worldwide and while it received mixed reviews from critics, it was generally deemed an improvement over its predecessor. == Cast == * Taissa Farmiga as Sister Irene ** Margot Bernazzi as young Irene * Jonas Bloquet as Maurice * Storm Reid as Sister Debra * Anna Popplewell as Kate * Bonnie Aarons as The Nun * Katelyn Rose Downey as Sophie * Suzanne Bertish as Madame Laurent * David Horovitch as Cardinal Conroy * Andrew Morgado provides the demonic voice * Pascal Aubert as Father Noiret * Maxime Elias-Menet as Jacques * LÃ©ontine d'Oncieu as Simone Additionally, Patrick Wilson and Vera Farmiga reprise their roles as Ed and Lorraine Warren respectively in the mid-credits scene, using a scene cut from The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It. ==References== Category:2023 horror movies Category:American horror movies
